Lumber Kings]]''' (CJHL)\t\t\n|[[St-J\u00e9r\u00f4me Panthers]] (QJAAHL)\n|[[St-J\u00e9r\u00f4me Panthers]] (QJAAHL)\t\t\n|[[Saint-J\u00e9r\u00f4me, Quebec|St-J\u00e9r\u00f4me, QC]]\n|- bgcolor=\n|2008\t\n|'''[[Pictou County Crushers]]''' (MJAHL)\t\t\t\n|[[Pembroke Lumber Kings]] (CJHL)\n|[[Pictou County Crushers]] (MJAHL)\t\t\n|[[New Glasgow, Nova Scotia|New Glasgow, NS]]\n|- bgcolor=\n|2009\t\n|'''[[Summerside Western Capitals]]''' (MJAHL)\n|[[Dieppe Commandos]] (MJAHL)\n|[[Dieppe Commandos]] (MJAHL)\n|[[Moncton|Moncton, NB]]\n|-\n|2010\n|'''[[Brockville Braves]]''' (CJHL)\n|[[Pembroke Lumber Kings]] (CJHL)\n|[[Brockville Braves]] (CJHL)\n|[[Brockville|Brockville, ON]]\n|-\n|2011\n|'''[[Pembroke Lumber Kings]]''' (CCHL)\n|[[Longueuil College Francais]] (QJAAAHL)\n|[[Terrebonne Cobras]] (QJAAAHL) \n|[[Terrebonne, Quebec|Terrebonne, QC]]\n|-\n|2012\n|'''[[Woodstock Slammers]]''' (MHL)\n|[[Nepean Raiders]] (CCHL)\n|[[Ottawa Jr. Senators]] (CCHL)\n|[[Ottawa|Ottawa, ON]]\n|-\n|2013\n|'''[[Truro Bearcats]]''' ([[MJAHL|MHL]])\n|[[Summerside Western Capitals]] ([[MJAHL|MHL]])\n|[[Truro Bearcats]]\n|[[Truro, Nova Scotia|Truro, NS]]\n|-\n|2014\n|'''[[Carleton Place Canadians]]''' (CCHL)\n|[[St-J\u00e9r\u00f4me Panthers]] (QJAAAHL)\n|[[St-J\u00e9r\u00f4me Panthers]] (QJAAAHL)\n|[[Saint-J\u00e9r\u00f4me, Quebec|St-J\u00e9r\u00f4me, QC]]\n|-\n|[[2015 Fred Page Cup|2015]]\n|'''[[Carleton Place Canadians]]''' (CCHL)\n|[[Dieppe Commandos]] (MHL)\n|[[Cornwall Colts]] (CCHL)\n|[[Cornwall, Ontario|Cornwall, ON]]\n|-\n|[[2016 Fred Page Cup|2016]]\n|'''[[Carleton Place Canadians]]''' (CCHL)\n|[[Woodstock Slammers]] (MHL)\n|[[Woodstock Slammers]] (MHL)\n|[[Woodstock, New Brunswick|Woodstock, NB]]\n|-\n|[[2017 Fred Page Cup|2017]]\n|'''[[Terrebonne Cobras]]''' (QJHL)\n|[[Carleton Place Canadians]] (CCHL)\n|[[Terrebonne Cobras]] (QJHL)\n|[[Terrebonne, Quebec|Terrebonne, QC]]\n|-\n|[[2018 Fred Page Cup|2018]]\n|'''[[Ottawa Jr. Senators]]''' (CCHL)\n|[[Longueuil College Francais]] (QJHL)\n